data.description: Experience resort style living this Winter in the Isles of Collier Preserve.This tranquil villa located on one of the most coveted streets offers southern exposure overlooking picturesque waters. The open floorplan with volume & tray ceilings offers an abundance of natural light perfect for entertaining. Numerous upgrades include newer Bosch kitchen appliances, custom cabinetry up to the ceiling, wide plank porcelain tile, fireplace, high-end ceiling fans and light fixtures throughout. The primary bedroom provides views of the lake with upgraded tiled shower and custom walk-in closet. Guests take comfort in the split bedroom floorplan offering privacy. Office/Den perfect for remote work. Enjoy serene views from the spa & pool overlooking the lake. The screened lanai offers spacious lounging with Hurricane screens. Additional upgrades include brand new A/C, tankless water heater, impact glass & doors, plantation shutters, custom cabinetry in laundry room, and ample garage storage. The Isles offers a luxurious coastal lifestyle with amenities including resort style pool & spa, amazing food at Overlook Bar & Grill, fitness facility, biking & hiking trails, and events the entire year.
